Task 1: Four Purrfect Gallery (Image Gallery Project)
This task focuses on creating a responsive cat image gallery with category filters, hover effects, and a clean visual layout.
The project showcases different cat breeds and allows users to view images interactively.
It is developed using front-end web technologies and structured for easy navigation.
The gallery adapts well to different screen sizes and devices.
This task demonstrates basic web design, layout structuring, and user interaction.

GitHub Repository Link:
https://github.com/Lavanya11-blip/four-purrfect-gallery:
